title: Iowa Governor Defends Not Ordering Shelter-in-Place: Maybe Dr. Fauci 'Doesn't Have All the Information'
description: Governor Kim Reynolds argued that perhaps federal health care officials like Dr. Anthony Fauci "can't just look at a map" and make such demands.
content:
Iowa Governor Kim Reynolds defended her decision not to order a shelter-in-place for state residents amid the coronavirus pandemic, arguing that perhaps federal health care officials like Dr. Anthony Fauci "can't just look at a map" and make such demands.
